Articles.Content:
Anyone heard of the 'Fan-Wing'? It's a neat concept, a bit... Convoluted, but very, very cool.

Wikilink:

http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FanWing

Seriously- take a look. The concept is.... Elegant, yet amazing.

Basically a part with good lift, fan animation and some thrust.

Doesn't fan-wings have strange stalling properties though.
